profile_summary: As a seasoned developer with expertise in TypeScript, C, and C++, I leverage my technical skills to drive innovation in AI engineering, DevOps, and full-stack development. With a strong background as a former FOSS Lead and CTO, I have cultivated a professional network of 148 followers and actively contribute to the development community through my 94 public repositories. I'm passionate about exploring the intersections of technology, particularly in GenAI, and collaborating with like-minded individuals to push the boundaries of what's possible.
